org.xlattice.util

Class ArrayStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.util.ArrayStack
  • Deprecated.

    public class ArrayStack
extends java.lang.Object
    A faster Stack class. No internal synchronization, so must be externally synchronized if used in a multi-threaded environment. THIS CLASS SHOULD BE REPLACED WITH util.Stack IN ALL USING CODE.
    Author:
    Jim Dixon
